(834, '1', '3', 'A', 'FK018', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 1A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>09.00 - 11.00</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS !&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. THERE ARE ....... STUDENTS IN THE CLASSROOM.&nbsp; (MANY,MUCH, LITTLE, ANY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. THAT WOMAN&nbsp; IS ....... PERSON.&nbsp; &nbsp;(BEAUTY, BEAUTIFUL, BEAUTIFY, BEAUTIFULLY)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. MOTHER NEEDS ....... SALT IN THE MEATBALL.&nbsp; &nbsp;(FEW, LITTLE, ANY, MANY)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. THAT LETTER WILL BE ....... TO HER SOON.&nbsp; &nbsp;(SEND, SENT, SENDING, TO SEND)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. THERE ARE MANY ....... IN THE WAREHOUSE.&nbsp; &nbsp;( MOUSE, MOUSES, MICE, MISE)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. DON&#39;T ....... ANGRY TO ME !&nbsp; &nbsp;(TO BE, BE, BEING, BEEN)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. ....... ON YOUR SEAT BESIDE ME !&nbsp; ( SIT, SITTING, TO SIT, SAT)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. STUDENTS DO THEIR HOMEWORK ........&nbsp; &nbsp; (MYSELF, YOURSELVES, HERSELF, THEMSELVES&nbsp; )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. SHE MAKES THAT CAKE EVERY SUNDAY ........&nbsp; &nbsp; (MYSELF, YOURSELF, HIMSELF, HERSELF)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. THAT GRANDFATHER HAS ....... TEETH NOW.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(MUCH, LITTLE, FEW, ANY&nbsp; )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE INTO ENGLISH !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. ADA BANYAK PIRING DI DAPUR.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. IBU PERLU SEDIKIT TELUR UNTUK KUE ITU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. PAMAN SAYA PUNYA SEBUAH MEJA YANG BESAR.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. PITON ADALAH SEEKOR ULAR YANG PANJANG DAN BESAR.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. ADA BANYAK DAUN DI TANAH.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. KURSI ITU DIBUAT DARI KAYU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. JANGAN MALU UNTUK BERTANYA !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. BERIKAN SAYA SEDIKIT INFORMASI !&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. DIA MENULIS SURAT ITU SENDIRI.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. ADA BANYAK NYAMUK DI RUMAH MU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2022/2023', '4', '1', '2023-01-03 01:03:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(835, '1', '3', 'B', 'FK018', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 1B</p>\r\n\r\n<p>18.30 - 20.30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. DON&#39;T .......ANGRY TO ME !&nbsp; &nbsp;(BE, TO BE, BEING, BEEN )&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. ....... ON THE SEAT BESIDE ME !&nbsp; &nbsp;(SIT, SITTING,&nbsp; SAT, TO SIT )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. STUDENTS DO THE HOMEWORK .......&nbsp; &nbsp; (HERSELF, THEMSELVES, YOURSELVES, MYSELF )&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. SHE MAKES THAT CAKE EVERY SUNDAY ........&nbsp; &nbsp;(HERSELF, HIMSELF, MYSELF, YOURSELF )&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. THAT GRANDFATHER HAS ....... TEETH NOW.&nbsp; &nbsp;(MUCH, LITTLE, FEW, ANY)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. THERE ARE ....... STUDENTS IN THE CLASSROOM.&nbsp; &nbsp;(MANY, MUCH, LITTLE, ANY)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. THAT WOMAN IS A ....... PERSON.&nbsp; (BEAUTY, BEAUTIFUL, BEAUTIFY, BEAUTIFULLY )&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. MOTHER NEEDS ....... SALT IN THE MEATBALL.&nbsp; &nbsp;(FEW, LITTLE, ANY, MANY&nbsp; )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. THAT LETTER WILL BE ....... TO HER SOON.&nbsp; &nbsp;(SEND&nbsp; SENDING, SENT, TO SEND )&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. THERE ARE MANY ....... IN THE WAREHOUSE.&nbsp; (MOUSE, MOUSES, MICE, MISE)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE INTO ENGLISH !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. MEJA ITU DIBUAT DARI KAYU.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. JANGAN MALU UNTUK BERTANYA !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. BERIKAN SAYA BEBERAPA INFORMASI !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. DIA MENULIS SURAT ITU SENDIRI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. ADA BANYAK KERBAU DI SAWAH.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. ADA SEDIKIT PIRING DI DAPUR.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. IBU PERLU BANYAK TELUR UNTUK KUE ITU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. PAMAN SAYA PUNYA SEBUAH MEJA KECIL DI RUMAHNYA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. PITON ADALAH SEEKOR ULAR YANG BESAR DAN PANJANG.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. ADA BANYAK DAUN DI TANAH.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK&nbsp; -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&