(1437, '1', '4', 'A', 'FK019', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 2A (UTS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. MOTHER LIKES WEARING A GREEN - _______ DRESS, ( COLOUR, COLOURING, COLOURED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. THERE ARE MANY _______ PEOPLE IN THAT MEETING.( EDUCATE, EDUCATING, EDUCATED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. WE _______ WATCHING MOVIE IN THE CINEMA&nbsp; LAST NIGHT. ( ARE, WERE, IS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. SHE _______ WORKED IN THAT COMPANY IN THE YEAR OF 2000. ( HAVE, HAS, HAD )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. STUDENTS MUST STUDY _______ TO FACE THE FINAL EXAMINATION. ( DILIGENT, DILIGENTLY, DILIGENCE )&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. THE BIG MAN CAN BRING THAT TABLE _______. ( STRONG, STRONGNESS, STRONGLY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. _______ BOOKS IN THE LIBRARY CAN ADD OUR KNOWLEDGE. ( READ, READING, TO READ )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. FATHER ENJOYS _______ A BEAUTIFUL VIEW. ( DRAW, DREW, DRAWING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. I LIKE THAT GOLDEN - _______ GIRL OVERTHERE. ( HEART, HEARTING, HEARTED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. PUPPET IS A VERY _______ SHOW IN CENTRAL JAVA.&nbsp; ( ATTRACT, ATTRACTING, ATTRACTED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE INTO INDONESIAN AND FIND&nbsp; 4 HOMOPHONES !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IF YOU INTEND TO VISIT TAMAN SAFARI, WE CAN&nbsp; SIMPLY GO BY PUBLIC CAR ON EITHER WEEK END OR WEEKDAYS. AS THE COMPANY WILL PROVIDE YOU WITH ITS OWN BUSES TO TRAVEL IN THE LOCATION. ON WEEKDAYS ONLY FEWS OF PEOPLE VISIT THAT PLACE. BUT ON WEEKEND IT WILL BE PACKED BY VISITORS COMING FROM ALL PARTS OF THE COUNTRY, EVEN FOREIGN COUNTRIES. CHOOSE A SEAT ABOUT THE WINDOW, SO THAT YOU CAN SEE THE VIEWS CLEARLY. SIT ON YOUR OWN SEAT WITHOUT MOVING. IN ORDER NOT TO DISTURB THE OTHERS. IF YOU DRIVE YOUR OWN CAR , KEEP IN LINE WHILE IN THE LOCATION. OTHERWISE YOU WILL BE ENDANGERED BY WILD AND FIERCE ANIMALS LIKE LION, TIGER, BEAR AND MANY OTHERS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK&nbsp; -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2022/2023', '3', '1', '2023-04-01 01:21:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
