(1865, '1', '2', 'C', 'GC320', 'AH1010', '<p>Terangkan dengan singkat, pasangan konsep berikut ini. Terangkan pula perbedaan atau/dan persamaan pasangan konsep tersebut !</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>&#39;&#39;Operating System Components&#39;&#39; vs.&#39;&#39;Operating System Services&#39;&#39;.</li>\r\n	<li>&#39;&#39;Distributed Systems&#39;&#39; vs. &#39;&#39;Clustered Systems&#39;&#39;</li>\r\n	<li>&#39;&#39;Client Server System&#39;&#39; vs. &#39;&#39;Peer&shy;to&shy;peer system&#39;&#39;.</li>\r\n	<li>Multithread Model: &#39;&#39;One to One&#39;&#39; vs. &#39;&#39;Many to Many&#39;&#39;</li>\r\n	<li>&#39;&#39;Microkernels&#39;&#39; vs.&#39;&#39;Virtual Machines&#39;&#39;.</li>\r\n	<li>&#39;&#39;Deadlock&#39;&#39; vs. &#39;&#39;Starvation&#39;&#39;</li>\r\n	<li>Storage System: &#39;&#39;Volatile&#39;&#39; vs. &#39;&#39;Non&shy;volatile&#39;&#39;</li>\r\n	<li>Software License: &ldquo;Free Software&rdquo; vs. &ldquo;Copyleft</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '', '2022/2023', '3', '1', '2023-05-03 01:43:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
