(2464, '1', '4', 'C', 'FK019', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 2 C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE A CORRECT WORD IN THE PARENTHESIS !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. MOTHER LIKES WEARING A BROWN - _______ DRESS FOR THE PARTY. ( COLOUR, COLOURING, COLOURED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2, THERE ARE MANY ________ PEOPLE IN THE MEETING. ( EDUCATE, EDUCATING, EDUCATED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. WE _______ WATCHING A MOVIE IN THE CINEMA LAST WEEK.&nbsp; ( ARE, WERE, WAS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. THEY _______ WORKED IN THAT COMPANY IN THE YEAR OF 2010. ( HAVE, HAS, HAD )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. STUDENTS MUST STUDY ________ TO FACE THE FINAL TEST. ( DILIGENT, DILIGENCE, DILIGENTLY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. THE BIG MAN CAN BRING THAT CUPBAORD _______. ( STRONG, STRONGLY, STRONGNESS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. _______&nbsp; MANY BOOKS IN THE LIBRARY CAN ADD OUR KNOWLEDGE. ( READ, READING, READS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. MY UNCLE ENJOYS _______ A BEAUTIFUL VIEWS. ( DRAW, DREW, DRAWING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9 I LIKE THAT GOLDEN - _______ GIRL OVERTHERE . ( HEART, HEARTING, HEARTED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. PUPPET IS A VERY _______ SHOW IN CENTRAL JAVA. ( ATTRACT, ATTRACTED, ATTRACTING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II,&nbsp; READ CAREFULLY !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WHEN I VISITED AMBOM, I FOUND A KIND OF STRANGE FOOD, NAMELY KRUPUK PALOLO. YOU WILL HARDLY BELIEVE THAT IT IS MADE OF WORM NAMED PALOLO. AT FIRST I COULDN&#39;T EAT IT, BUT SLOWLY I COULD ADAPT MY TASTE TO IT. IF YOU WANT TO TEST THE TASTE OF KRUPUK PALOLO. DON&#39;T DRINK COOL WATER AFTERWARDS, OTHERWISE YOU WILL GET SICK, DRINK HOT OR WARM WATER INSTEAD. WHEN IT MOVES INDIVIDUALLY, PALOLO MAYBE VERY HIDIOUS AS IT IS A REAL WORM, BUT IN COLONY THEY ARE LIKE A HUGE OF ROPES OR NOODLES. IF YOU TAKE AND STRAIN A HEALTHY PALOLO, IT WILL BE VERY ELASTIC AND STURDY LIKE AN EEL, BUT AN ILL PALOLO WILL EASILY BREAK. AND IF YOU HAVE COOKED AND SPICED THEM TO BE MADE KRUPUK, YOU WILL GET A STRANGE BUT HIGHLY NUTRITIOUS FOOD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A. TRANSLATE INTO INDONESIAN !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B. FIND 5 HOMOPHONES !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p