(2525, '1', '3', 'A', 'FK018', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 1A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. HE _______ A TEACHER NOW.&nbsp; ( IS, ARE, WAS, WERE )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. THEY _______ IN THE CAMPUS&nbsp; TWO DAYS AGO.&nbsp; ( IS, ARE, WAS, WERE )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. MOTHER _______ A RED DRESS LAST YEAR.&nbsp; ( WEAR, WEARS, WORE, WORN )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. _______ HE STUDY ENGLISH EVERY TIME ?&nbsp; ( DO, DOES, DID, IS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. _______ YOUR FATHER GO TO BANDUNG LAST WEEK ?&nbsp; (DO, DOES, DID, IS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. WE _______ ENGLISH IN THE CLASS YESTERDAY. ( SPEAK, SPEAKS, SPOKE, SPEAKING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. BEFORE _______ HOME, LET&#39;S PRAY TOGETHER !&nbsp; ( GO, GOING, WENT, GONE )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. THEY GO TO SCHOOL AFTER _______ BREAKFAST.&nbsp; ( HAVE, HAS, HAVING, HAD)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. THERE ISN&#39;T _______ SALT IN THE BOWL. ( SOME,&nbsp; ANY, MANY, FEW )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. STUDENTS NEED _______ BOOKS TO READ.( SOME, ANY, MUCH, LITTLE )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE AND MAKE +, -, ? !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. KITA ADALAH NELAYAN DI DESA INI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. DIA PERGI KE PASAR SETIAP HARI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. MEREKA MENGUNJUNGI KEBUN RAYA BOGOR TAHUN LALU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. ANAK-ANAK AKAN MEMBACA BUKU CERITA INI BESOK.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. ADA BEBERAPA ORANG DILAPANGAN ITU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK&nbsp; -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2023-10-27 01:02:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
