>\r\n			<p>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>dismissal</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:144px\">\r\n			<p>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:144px\">\r\n			<p>insecure</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>termination</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:144px\">\r\n			<p>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:144px\">\r\n			<p>flexible</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Match the sentence beginnings (1-5) with the correct endings (a-e). The sentences all contain words from A and B article.&nbsp; (15)</l