(3780, '1', '3', 'A', 'FK018', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 1A (UAS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. THERE ARE _______ CHILDREN IN THAT HOUSE. ( MANY, LITTLE, MUCH, ANY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. THIS GIRL IS A _______ PERSON IN THAT FAMILY. ( BEAUTY, BEAUTIFUL, BEAUTIFY, BEAUTIFULLY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. MOTHER BOUGHT _______ SUGAR IN THAT SHOP.&nbsp; ( FEW, LITTLE, ANY, MANY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. THAT CAKE WILL BE _______ TO THE NEXT NEIGHBOR SOON, ( SEND, SENDS, SENT, SENDED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. THERE ARE MANY _______ IN OUR SCHOOL. ( MOUSE, MOUSES, MICE, MISE )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. DON&#39;T _______ ANGRY TO YOUR FATHER !&nbsp; ( TO BE, BE, BEEN, BEING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.&nbsp; _______ ON THE CHAIR BESIDE YOUR FREIND ! ( SIT, SAT, SITS, SITTING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. MY FRIENDS DO THE HOMEWORK&nbsp; _______.&nbsp; ( MYSELF, HERSELF, OURSELVES, THEMSELVES )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. HE MADE THE CUPBOARD LAST YEAR&nbsp; _______. ( HERSELF, HIMSELF, ITSELF, THEMSELVES )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. MY GRANDFATHER HAS&nbsp; _______ TEETH NOW.&nbsp; ( MUCH, LITTLE, FEW, ANY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE INTO ENGLISH !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. ADA BANYAK MANGKUK DIATAS MEJA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. IBU MEMBAWA BANYAK TELUR UNTUK MEMBUAT KUE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. TETANGGA SAYA MEMBUAT LEMARI BESAR BULAN LALU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. GAJAH ADALAH SEEKOR BINATANG YANG BESAR DAN KUAT.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. ADA BANYAK ANGSA DI DANAU ITU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. MEJA KECIL ITU DIBUAT DARI KAYU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. JANGAN MALU UNTUK MENJAWAB PERTANYAAN !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. BERIKAN SAYA SEDIKIT INFORMASI YANG BENAR !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. MEREKA BERBICARA TENTANG MASALAH ITU SENDIRI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. ADA BANYAK KERBAU DI SAWAH PAMANMU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK&nbsp; -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '4', '1', '2023-12-29 01:16:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
