; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>Promosi Penjualan</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:88px\">\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li><em>Coupons </em>(kupon)</li>\r\n				<li><em>Rebates </em>(Potongan harga)</li>\r\n				<li><em>Price Pack </em>(Harga Paket)</li>\r\n				<li>Sampel</li>\r\n				<li><em>Premium</em></li>\r\n				<li><em>Cashback</em></li>\r\n				<li><em>Continuity programs</em></li>\r\n				<li>Kontes dan undian (<em>Contest and sweepstakes</em>)</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57px\">\r\n			<p>Likert</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:76px\">\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>PPJ1</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>PPJ2</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>PPJ3</li>\r\n				<li>PPJ4</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>PPJ5</li>\r\n				<li>PPJ6</li>\r\n				<li>PPJ7</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>PPJ8</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:132px\">\r\n			<p>Menurut Kotler (2007:266), promosi adalah elemen penting untuk menginformasikan produk dengan waktu tertentu, yang dibuat untuk memikat konsumen untuk membeli dengan jumlah yang banyak.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:38px\">\r\n			<p>4.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:138px