(4694, '1', '3', 'C', 'IS402', 'HJ9101', '<p>The pros of the waterfall methodology (design must be specification on paper before programing begins, long time between system proposal and delivery on new system, maximizes changes to requirements as project progress<strong>,</strong> identifies systems requirements long before programming begins)</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-02-17 08:55:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4695, '1', '3', 'C', 'IS402', 'HJ9101', '<p>Three RAD catagories (phased development, prototyping, thru-away prototyping), (Phased deployment, Prototyping, Throw-away prototyping),(Phased development, Prototyping, Thru-away prototyping),(Phase development, Protoptyping, Throw-away prototyping),(Phased development, Prototyping, Throw-away prototyping).</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-02-17 08:56:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4696, '1', '3', 'C', 'IS402', 'HJ9101', '<p>Users can identify needed changes and refine real requirement. This is a pros of metodology ....(waterfall, agile, prototyping, parallel)</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-02-17 08:56:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4697, '1', '3', 'C', 'IS402', 'HJ9101', '<p>3 langkah analisis (Analysis strategy, Recomendation gathering, System proposal),(Information gathering, Analysis strategy, Proposal development),(Analysis strategy, Requirements gathering, System proposal),(Planning strategy, Requiremnts gathering, System proposal)</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-02-17 08:57:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4698, '1', '3', 'C', 'IS402', 'HJ9101', '<p>Metodology Prototyping paling cocok untuk sistem yang ...(unclear user requirement<strong>, </strong>a short time schedule, schedule visibility, unfamiliar technology, complex, reliable, unclear user requirement, complex, schedule visibility, unfamiliar technology, a shortime schedule, reliable)</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-02-17 08:57:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
