(4807, '5', '6', 'C', 'SMBB128', 'FJ2072', '<p>1. Jelaskan prinsip-prinsip etika bisnis !&nbsp; (bobot 20&nbsp; &nbsp;)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Jelaskan&nbsp; perbedaan dua aliran teleologis&nbsp; : egoisme dan utilitarianisme&nbsp; !&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ( bobot&nbsp; &nbsp;10 )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Jelaskan hubungan keterkaitan antara etika bisnis dan etika profesi! ( bobot&nbsp; 10&nbsp; )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Jelaskan pendapat Anda apakah etika dalam bisnis dapat berubah atau ada aturan baku yang mengaturnya? ( bobot&nbsp; &nbsp;10)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Jelaskan&nbsp; pendapat Anda mengenai tingkat kepedulian antara pelaku bisnis terhadap etika bisnis ! ( bobot&nbsp; 10)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.&nbsp; Jelaskan dampak negatif jika etika bisnis tidak diterapkan secara maksimal dalam lingkungan bisnis !&nbsp; ( bobot 20&nbsp; &nbsp;)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.Jelaskan pendapat Anda jika suatu perusahaan mematuhi berbagai ketentuan dalam bidang etika bisnis, maka perolehan keuntungannya akan terjadi penurunan. Berikan penjelasan Anda dengan contohnya !&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ( bobot&nbsp; 20)</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-23 03:19:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4808, '5', '6', 'C', 'SMPB220', 'FJ2072', '<p>1. Jelaskan hambatan-hambatan atau penghalang kelancaran berkomunikasi dalam dunia bisnis!&nbsp; (bobot 20&nbsp; &nbsp;)<br />\r\n2.&nbsp; Jelaskan dimaksud dengan perencanaan dan pengorganisasian pesan-pesan bisnis&nbsp; !&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ( bobot&nbsp; &nbsp;10 )<br />\r\n3. Jelaskan teori W.Schramm : The conditions of success in communication &ldquo; , berikan penerapannya dalam konteks komunikasi bisnis! ( bobot&nbsp; 20&nbsp; )<br />\r\n4.&nbsp; Jelaskan hubungan presentasi bisnis dan komunikasi bisnis! Berikan contoh! ( bobot&nbsp; &nbsp;10)<br />\r\n5. Jelaskan beberapa teknik mendengarkan secara efektif (effective listening), dan berikan contoh dalam konteks dunia bisnis&nbsp; ! ( bobot&nbsp; 20)<br />\r\n6. Jelaskan pentingnya memahami komunikasi bisnis lintas budaya, berikan contohnya !&nbsp; ( bobot 10&nbsp; &nbsp;)<br />\r\n7.Jelaskan pengaruh komunikasi bisnis dalam pengembangan dunia bisnis!&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ( bobot&nbsp; 10 )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-23 03:21:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4809, '1', '4', 'A', 'FK019', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 2A (UTS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.THAT BIG MAN CAN BRING THAT TABLE _______.&nbsp; ( STRONG, STRONGER, STRONGLY )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. _______MANY BOOKS IN THE LIBRARY CAN ADD OUR KNOWLEDGE. ( READ, READED, READING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. MY UNCLE ENJOYS _______ A BEAUTIUL MOUNTAIN. ( DRAW, DREW, DRAWING )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. WE LIKE A GOLDEN - _______ GIRL OVERTHERE. ( HEART, HEARTING, HEARTED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. TELKOM IS ONE OF THE STATE - _______ COMPANY IN INDONESIA. ( OWN, OWNING, OWNED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. MY SISTER LIKES WEARING A GREEN - _______ DRESS.&nbsp; ( COLOUR, COLOURING, COLOURED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. THERE ARE MANY _______ PEOPLE IN THAT MEETING. ( EDUCATE, EDUCATING, EDUCATED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. THEY _______LIVED IN JAKARTA&nbsp; FOR TEN YEARS IN THE YEAR OF 2010. ( HAVE, HAS, HAD )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. WE _______ WATCHING THE SCARE MOVIE IN THAT CINEMA LAST NIGHT. ( ARE, WERE, WAS, IS&nbsp; )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. STUDENTS MUST STUDY _______ TO FACE THE FINAL EXAM. ( HARD, HARDLY, HARDER )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE INTO INDONESIAN AND FIND 5 HOMOPHONES 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TO MEET THE NEED OF NUTRITIOUS FOOD DIVESIFICATION, PEOPLE MUST CONSUME MEAT, DESPITE CONSUMING TOO MUCH MEAT, MAY CAUSE COWS OR OTHER LIVESTOCK&nbsp; POPULATION DECREASE RAPIDLY. VEGETARIANS DON&#39;T EAT MEAT, BUT I MYSELF EAT IT. DO YU KNOW THAT BESIDES BEING MADE MANY KINDS OF PRODUCTS LIKE BAGS, SHOES, AND MANY OTHERS, LEATHER RAW MATERIALS TAKEN FROM COWS MAY ALSO BE MADE KRUPUK KULIT. AND FOR FUTURE BUSINESS, KRUPUK KULIT IS VERY POTENTIAL TO LEAD THE RAW - PRODUCT EXPORT COMODITY INCREASE FOR INDONESIA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK&nbsp; -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-25 01:07:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4810, '1', '4', 'B', 'FK019', 'NH9901', '<p>ENGLISH 2B (UTS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I. CHOOSE THE CORRECT ONE IN THE PARENTHESIS !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. TELKOM IS ONE OF THE STATE - _______ COMPANY IN INDONESIA. ( OWN, OWNING, OWNED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. I LIKE A GOLDEN - _______ GIRL IN MY CLASS. ( HEART, HERTING, HEARTED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. MY UNCLE ENJOYS _______&nbsp; A BEAUTIFUL MOUNTAIN IN BOGOR. ( DRAW, DRAWING, DREW )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. _______ IN THE RIVER IS MY FAVOURITE HOBBY. ( FISH, FISHING, FISHED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. THAT FAT MAN CAN BRING THE CUPBOARD _______. ( STRONG, STRONGLY, STRONGER)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. STUDENDS MUST STUDY _______ TO FACE THE FINAL EXAM. (HARD, HARDLY, HARDER )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. SHE _______ LIVED IN JAKARTA&nbsp; FOR TEN YEARS IN THE YEAR OF 2010. ( HAVE, HAS, HAD )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. WE _______ WATCHING THE SCARE MOVIE IN THAT CINEMA LAST NIGHT. ( ARE, WERE, WAS, IS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. THERE ARE MANY _______ PEOPLE IN THAT MEETING. ( EDUCATE, EDUCATING, EDUCATED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. MY SISTER LIKES WEARING A GREEN - _______ DRESS. ( COLOUR, COLOURING, COLOURED )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>II. TRANSLATE INTO INDONESIAN AND FIND 5 HOMOPHONES !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TO MEET THE NEED OF NUTRITIOUS FOOD DIVERSIFICATION, PEOPLE MUST CONSUME MEAT, DESPITE&nbsp; CONSUMING TOO MUCH MEAT, MAY CAUSE COWS OR OTHER LIVESTOCK POPULATION DECREASE RAPIDLY. VEGETARIANS DON&#39;T EAT MEAT, BUT I MYSELF EAT IT. DO YOU KNOW THAT BESIDES BEING MADE MANY KINDS OF PRODUCTS LIKE BAGS, SHOES, AND MANY OTHERS, LEATHER RAW MATERIALS TAKEN FROM COWS MAY ALSO BE MADE KRUPUK KULIT. AND FOR FUTURE BUSINESS, KRUPUK KULIT IS VERY POTENTIAL TO LEAD THE RAW - PRODUCT EXPORT COMODITY INCREASE FOR INDONESIA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------&nbsp; GOOD&nbsp; LUCK&nbsp; -------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-25 01:37:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4811, '1', '8', 'D', 'IS317', 'EB2202', '<p>Basic Sistem Enterprise :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a.&nbsp;Apakah ERP itu sama dengan Enterprise System ? Jelaskan secara detail jawaban anda</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b.&nbsp;Ada beberapa point karakteristik dari Sistem Enterprise, Analisa dan Jelaskan&nbsp; secara detail minimal 4 point <strong>Karakteristik yang menurut anda paling penting / vital</strong> dari Sistem Enterprise tersebut.</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-26 12:06:02', '2024-04-26 12:13:14'),
(4812, '1', '8', 'D', 'IS317', 'EB2202', '<p>Customer Relationship Management :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a.&nbsp;Menurut Analisa anda, apa saja hambatan utama atau tantangan Ketika kita akan menerapkan CRM dalam Perusahaan ? Jelaskan jawaban anda secara detail</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b. Studi Kasus :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Perusahaan &ldquo;DOLAN&rdquo; adalah perusahaan yang bergerak pada bidang Game Online yang sudah berjalan selama 2 Tahun. Mereka ingin mengukur keberhasilan program layanan pelanggan mereka dengan melihat beberapa metrik utama dalam CRM. Berikut ini adalah informasi yang terkait dari performa Perusahaan &ldquo;DOLAN&rdquo; :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Jumlah Gamers awal periode (Awal Bulan) : 1500 Gamers</li>\r\n	<li>Jumlah Gamers akhir periode (Akhir Bulan) : 1600 Gamers</li>\r\n	<li>Jumlah Gamers yang keluar (Tidak Langganan) dalam 1 Bulan : 200 Gamers</li>\r\n	<li>Jumlah Gamers yang memberikan nilai Puas dalam survei: 100 Gamers</li>\r\n	<li>Jumlah Gamers yang memberikan nilai Netral &nbsp;dalam survei: 350 Gamers</li>\r\n	<li>Jumlah Gamers yang memberikan nilai Tidak Puas dalam survei: 50 Gamers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Adapun target CRM Scorecard yang sudah ditetapkan oleh Perusahaan &ldquo;DOLAN&rdquo; telampir pada tabel dibawah :</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:692px\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#c1e4f5; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:138px\">\r\n			<p><strong>Metrik</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#c1e4f5; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:159px\">\r\n			<p><strong>Target</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#c1e4f5; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:387px\">\r\n			<p><strong>Keterangan</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>Retensi Pelanggan</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:159px\">\r\n			<p>Minimal 90 %</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:387px\">\r\n			<p>Memastikan sebagian besar pelanggan tetap berlangganan setiap bulan.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>Churn Rate</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:159px\">\r\n			<p>Maksimal 5 %</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:387px\">\r\n			<p>Mengurangi jumlah pelanggan yang berhenti langganan.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>Customer Satisfaction</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:159px\">\r\n			<p>Minimal &nbsp;50 %</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:387px\">\r\n			<p>Meningkatkan kepuasan pelanggan terhadap layanan yang diberikan.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:138px\">\r\n			<p>Net Promoter Score (NPS)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:159px\">\r\n			<p>Minimal 20 %</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-left:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-right:1px solid #e3e3e3; border-top:1px solid #e3e3e3; width:387px\">\r\n			<p>Memastikan sebagian besar pelanggan bersedia merekomendasikan produk/layanan kepada orang lain.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Dari Contoh studi kasus diatas tentukan :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nilai dari <strong>Retensi Pelanggan, Churn Rate, Customer Satisfaction, dan NPS </strong>perusahaan &ldquo;Dolan&rdquo; dan Analisa apa saja strategi yang perlu dilakukan / di tingkatkan / diperbaiki oleh Perusahaan &ldquo;DOLAN&rdquo; dengan perbandingan CRM Scorecard yang sudah ditetapkan. (Jawaban bisa ditulis di kertas lalu diupload jika kesulitan)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-26 12:10:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4813, '1', '8', 'D', 'IS317', 'EB2202', '<p>Basic Supply Chain Management (SCM) :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dalam mengelola Supply Chain Management (SCM) ada 2 kendala utama yang selalu dihadapi oleh perusahaan yaitu : <strong>Kompleksitas</strong> dan <strong>Ketidakpastian</strong>. Analisa 2 kendala ini dari sudut pandang komponen CRM khususnya pada Industri Makanan namun bergantung &nbsp;dari bahan baku import dan contoh solusinya dari kendala tersebut. (Jelaskan dengan Bahasa, Analisa dan Logika Kalian)</p>\r\n', '', '2023/2024', '3', '1', '2024-04-26 12:12:15', '2024-04-26 12:12:41'),
